channel.title: YanScape 2.7
channel.description:
Please, don't comment bad this is my first source. I've been working on it for almost 2 months and it's starting to shape up. Now I know in this source there is some bugs needed to be fixed but most of it is really nice, so we will start with the features. 100% Fishing Farming Thieving RuneCrafting WoodCutting Smithing not 100% will be in final version! Mining about 100% Firemaking 100% Cooking around 98% Crafting 65% Fletching 0% Agility 0% Slayer
Enough with that now we have some pictures for your enjoyment
